data.description: Assumable Loan with a 2.5% rate!  Save your buyer hundreds of dollars on monthly payments. Row-End Townhome in a with lots of great amenities: swimming pool, play grounds, fitness center, clubhouse, and within walking distance to Cougar park.  2 yr old furnace and A/C. Fully enclose private back patio great for a BBQ, or for your pet.  New garage door in 2022. Large master bedroom and bathroom. Enjoy the open grassy common areas with shade from the many mature trees. Newer stainless steel appliances.  Come soak in the sun at the pool during the summer months.  Located within minutes to lots of shopping, the sports complex, Jordan's Landing, Mountain View golf course and much more.
